OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Mainly dry with clear spells
OL,8,Fovernight especially in the east but
OL,9,Fsome showers will affect Dumfries and
OL,10,FGalloway later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA mostly dry and sunny start
OL,13,Fto the day. Then clouds building,
OL,14,Fperhaps bringing one or two light
OL,15,Fshowers, the east then brightening
OL,16,Fagain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
